I could get dragged in too.

36
00:03:38,000 --> 00:03:39,760
So that's what this is.

37
00:03:40,240 --> 00:03:41,240
Got it.

38
00:03:41,240 --> 00:03:42,400
Let's step aside.

39
00:03:59,640 --> 00:04:00,800
Today,

40
00:04:00,800 --> 00:04:03,120
I'm giving you one last chance.

41
00:04:03,120 --> 00:04:06,080
As long as you're willing to
be my sweet wife,

42
00:04:06,080 --> 00:04:07,440
I can keep the child
and discard the mother.

43
00:04:07,440 --> 00:04:08,360
So that you can

44
00:04:08,360 --> 00:04:09,520
become Fang Yao's child's mother.

45
00:04:10,440 --> 00:04:12,240
How twisted is your logic

46
00:04:12,240 --> 00:04:13,760
to say something so shameless?

47
00:04:13,760 --> 00:04:14,640
Fang Yao has no shame,

48
00:04:14,640 --> 00:04:15,520
and you're just as awful.

49
00:04:15,520 --> 00:04:17,080
You two are a perfect match.

50
00:04:17,080 --> 00:04:18,040
Stop bothering me.

51
00:04:18,040 --> 00:04:19,000
I... I...

52
