You know what,

53
00:04:25,080 --> 00:04:25,920
Huo Xiao's only protecting you

54
00:04:25,920 --> 00:04:28,040
for your shares

55
00:04:28,600 --> 00:04:30,160
and your charm.

56
00:04:30,160 --> 00:04:32,040
If you weren't the daughter-in-law of
Song family,

57
00:04:32,040 --> 00:04:32,920
if you weren't An Ning,

58
00:04:32,920 --> 00:04:34,320
do you think he'd even look at you?

59
00:04:34,320 --> 00:04:35,240
Watch your mouth!

60
00:04:36,520 --> 00:04:37,880
He's him, and I'm me.

61
00:04:37,880 --> 00:04:39,880
Stop making your dirty assumptions.

62
00:04:43,960 --> 00:04:44,720
An Ning.

63
00:04:44,720 --> 00:04:45,520
An Ning!

64
00:04:50,120 --> 00:04:52,440
Somehow I ended up the lead
in this whole "stand-in" drama.

65
00:04:52,440 --> 00:04:53,600
And I'm actually
getting into the role.

66
00:04:58,040 --> 00:04:59,200
Her pregnancy timeline

67
00:04:59,880 --> 00:05:00,800
is fishy.

68
00:05:03,520 --> 00:05:04,560
I need your help

69
