It's nothing.

74
00:05:29,840 --> 00:05:31,320
I just want to be alone.

75
00:05:31,320 --> 00:05:32,800
Stop worrying about
my business from now on.

76
00:05:35,760 --> 00:05:37,320
Why say that all of a sudden?

77
00:05:37,320 --> 00:05:38,320
Whether it's a misunderstanding

78
00:05:38,320 --> 00:05:39,320
or a hidden reason,

79
00:05:40,320 --> 00:05:41,680
if you don't explain clearly,

80
00:05:42,480 --> 00:05:43,720
I'll stay and face it with you.

81
00:05:44,960 --> 00:05:46,000
Then let me ask you something.

82
00:05:46,920 --> 00:05:48,120
If you find out

83
00:05:48,120 --> 00:05:49,360
I'm not who you think I am,

84
00:05:49,760 --> 00:05:51,160
will you still treat me this way?

85
00:05:52,480 --> 00:05:53,240
Could it be...

86
00:05:53,760 --> 00:05:55,000
she remembered something?

87
00:05:56,360 --> 00:05:57,480
If you don't want to talk,
forget it.

88
00:05:57,480 --> 00:05:58,320
I don't need to know.

89
