Since the baby can't be saved,

101
00:06:53,680 --> 00:06:56,240
then let his death mean something.

102
00:07:07,360 --> 00:07:08,520
You asked me here,

103
00:07:08,520 --> 00:07:09,760
just to apologize?

104
00:07:09,760 --> 00:07:11,520
Or are you planning some new trick?

105
00:07:12,160 --> 00:07:13,760
I changed my mind.

106
00:07:14,280 --> 00:07:16,680
Bad luck like you.

107
00:07:16,680 --> 00:07:18,160
The sludge in a gutter.

108
00:07:18,160 --> 00:07:19,560
You're not even worthy to tie my shoes.

109
00:07:19,560 --> 00:07:21,040
And you expect me to say sorry?

110
00:07:21,040 --> 00:07:22,280
I suggest

111
00:07:22,280 --> 00:07:23,760
next time you go for a checkup,

112
00:07:24,160 --> 00:07:25,800
book a brain scan specially.

113
00:07:25,800 --> 00:07:27,200
Check if you've lost your sanity.

114
00:07:27,200 --> 00:07:28,160
And you?

115
00:07:28,640 --> 00:07:30,920
Like a woman
chasing attention everywhere.

116
00:07:30,920 --> 00:07:31,800
Ti Cha got tired of you.

117
00:07:31,800 --> 00:07:33,040
So you moved on to Huo Xiao.

118
00:07:33,040 --> 00:07:35,560
You think he'd want
damaged goods like you?

119
00:07:35,560 --> 00:07:36,760
Keep dreaming.

120
00:07:36,800 --> 00:07:37,840
What did you just say?

121
00:07:38,640 --> 00:07:39,760
Say it again.

122
00:07:39,760 --> 00:07:41,640
I said you're a shameless woman.

123
00:07:41,640 --> 00:07:42,760
A slut! An orphan!

124
00:07:46,840 --> 00:07:47,880
Trying to provoke me

125
00:07:48,240 --> 00:07:49,440
and looking for a chance to retaliate.

126
00:07:49,600 --> 00:07:50,800
Your little trick

127
00:07:50,800 --> 00:07:51,800
and cheap stunt

128
00:07:51,800 --> 00:07:52,840
are too easy to see through.

129
00:07:53,720 --> 00:07:55,200
I was just playing along,

130
00:07:55,600 --> 00:07:56,920
watching you act like a clown

131
00:07:56,920 --> 00:07:58,360
and waiting what else can you pull off.

132
00:07:58,360 --> 00:07:59,400
Take your time.

133
00:07:59,400 --> 00:08:00,440
I'm done playing.

134
00:08:06,200 --> 00:08:07,280
My child.

135
00:08:07,680 --> 00:08:08,880
An Ning.

136
00:08:08,880 --> 00:08:10,680
You've hurt my child!

137
00:08:11,520 --> 00:08:12,600
My child.

138
00:08:17,120 --> 00:08:18,720
My child.

139
00:08:22,720 --> 00:08:23,400
Yao.

140
00:08:23,720 --> 00:08:24,880
- My child.
- Yao.

141
00:08:25,200 --> 00:08:25,880
Yao.

142
00:08:25,880 --> 00:08:26,720
- Yao, what's wrong?
- Ti Cha.

143
00:08:26,720 --> 00:08:27,880
It was An Ning.

144
00:08:27,880 --> 00:08:30,240
It was An Ning who hurt our child.

145
00:08:30,240 --> 00:08:31,400
It hurts so much.

146
00:08:31,400 --> 00:08:32,920
Are you okay, Yao?

147
00:08:32,920 --> 00:08:34,040
Ti Cha.

148
00:08:34,040 --> 00:08:36,080
What should we do?

149
00:08:36,080 --> 00:08:38,280
Our baby is gone.

150
00:08:38,680 --> 00:08:40,280
It's all because of An Ning.

151
00:08:40,960 --> 00:08:42,480
My baby...

152
00:08:42,520 --> 00:08:44,760
[Hospital]

153
00:08:47,160 --> 00:08:47,960
Sweetheart.

154
00:08:48,840 --> 00:08:50,680
Are you in a lot of pain?

155
00:08:51,240 --> 00:08:52,720
