it won't hurt anymore.

156
00:08:53,520 --> 00:08:54,960
Mom will sing a lullaby for you.

157
00:08:54,960 --> 00:08:55,960
And tell you a bedtime story.

158
00:08:55,960 --> 00:08:57,160
Would you like that?

159
00:08:57,160 --> 00:08:59,040
She even gave up her own child,

160
00:08:59,040 --> 00:09:00,320
