161
00:09:00,680 --> 00:09:01,720
What a performance.

162
00:09:02,360 --> 00:09:03,880
Being a mistress is
such a waste of your talent.

163
00:09:04,400 --> 00:09:05,360
You should really be an actress.

164
00:09:05,360 --> 00:09:06,960
You did this to her,

165
00:09:06,960 --> 00:09:08,160
and you can still smile?

166
00:09:08,160 --> 00:09:09,760
You cold-hearted thing.

167
00:09:10,120 --> 00:09:11,800
You forget the pain
once the wound heals.

168
00:09:12,080 --> 00:09:13,840
Aren't you used to this kind of drama?

169
00:09:13,840 --> 00:09:15,280
You're slandering me!

170
00:09:15,280 --> 00:09:17,240
Would I ever harm my own child?

171
00:09:17,240 --> 00:09:17,800
Shameless woman.

172
00:09:18,240 --> 00:09:19,640
You owe me my child!

173
00:09:20,000 --> 00:09:21,200
Yao.

174
00:09:22,440 --> 00:09:24,120
Even I don't want to believe it.

175
00:09:24,120 --> 00:09:26,160
That a mother could hurt her own child.

176
00:09:26,160 --> 00:09:28,760
You've truly renewed my understanding
of human evil.

177
00:09:28,760 --> 00:09:30,520
If you truly loved your child,

178
00:09:30,800 --> 00:09:32,680
you wouldn't use him
as a stepping stone.

179
00:09:33,840 --> 00:09:36,120
How can you slander me like that?

180
00:09:36,920 --> 00:09:37,920
This child

181
00:09:37,920 --> 00:09:40,200
is part of my own flesh and blood.

182
00:09:41,280 --> 00:09:42,600
If An Ning isn't punished,

183
00:09:42,600 --> 00:09:44,800
I'll go join my wrongly dead child!

184
00:09:46,560 --> 00:09:47,240
Yao!

185
00:09:47,880 --> 00:09:50,040
Yao, Yao!

186
00:09:50,040 --> 00:09:50,720
Does it hurt?

187
00:09:50,720 --> 00:09:52,640
Yao, don't do something stupid.

188
00:09:52,640 --> 00:09:53,240
Yao.

189
00:09:53,240 --> 00:09:55,040
You heartless woman.

190
00:09:55,040 --> 00:09:57,040
You're literally a demon
crawled out of hell!

191
00:09:57,040 --> 00:09:58,760
I'll make your ancestors

192
00:09:58,760 --> 00:10:00,520
feel shame for your evil deeds!

193
00:10:01,120 --> 00:10:02,280
You...

194
00:10:02,280 --> 00:10:04,040
You're just jealous that

195
00:10:04,040 --> 00:10:06,000
Yao can carry on
the Song family line.

196
00:10:06,000 --> 00:10:08,200
That's why you came up with
such a vile scheme.

197
00:10:08,200 --> 00:10:08,760
You...

198
00:10:08,760 --> 00:10:11,080
You're a vicious woman
worse than beasts!

199
00:10:11,080 --> 00:10:12,960
You destroyed
the Song family's unborn child.

200
00:10:12,960 --> 00:10:14,720
Once you've taken the family punishment,

201
00:10:14,720 --> 00:10:16,360
you'll be handed over to the police!

202
00:10:17,040 --> 00:10:17,600
Steward!

203
00:10:17,600 --> 00:10:18,000
Yes.

204
00:10:18,280 --> 00:10:19,280
Dear, I'll do it!

205
00:10:19,920 --> 00:10:22,160
Birds of a feather flock together.

206
00:10:22,800 --> 00:10:25,600
So I've walked right into
a den of wolves.

207
00:10:28,160 --> 00:10:29,800
You're beyond saving now.

208
00:10:29,800 --> 00:10:30,840
Today,

209
00:10:30,840 --> 00:10:32,760
I'll show everyone
the ugly truth about you.

210
00:10:32,760 --> 00:10:33,840
You wicked woman.

211
00:10:33,840 --> 00:10:35,320
Still trying to argue
when your end is near.

212
00:10:35,320 --> 00:10:36,400
I'll beat you to death!

213
00:10:40,720 --> 00:10:41,760
About the baby,

214
00:10:42,160 --> 00:10:43,880
why not ask the prenatal doctor first.

215
00:10:46,040 --> 00:10:46,840
Come in.

216
00:10:52,640 --> 00:10:53,920
People's hearts can be bought,

217
00:10:54,880 --> 00:10:55,840
but it depends

218
00:10:56,280 --> 00:10:57,720
[Pay to the order of Fang Yao, $5,000]
on who pays more.

219
00:11:00,760 --> 00:11:01,280
This…

220
00:11:04,960 --> 00:11:05,640
Go ahead, speak.

221
00:11:07,960 --> 00:11:10,160
The fetus had already shown
signs of stalling.

222
00:11:10,160 --> 00:11:13,560
Chromosomes and progesterone
all showed clear abnormalities.

223
00:11:13,560 --> 00:11:14,920
There was no way to keep the baby.

224
00:11:15,160 --> 00:11:16,560
She got abortion pills from me.

225
00:11:16,560 --> 00:11:17,840
And paid me hush money.

226
00:11:17,840 --> 00:11:18,640
Yao.

227
00:11:20,280 --> 00:11:21,240
You can go out now.

228
00:11:23,120 --> 00:11:23,960
Dad.

229
00:11:24,560 --> 00:11:26,440
Now the truth is finally out.

230
00:11:26,440 --> 00:11:28,520
I want to see
how you'll make this right.

231
00:11:32,240 --> 00:11:34,120
Ti… Ti Cha.

232
00:11:34,120 --> 00:11:34,800
I… I…

233
00:11:34,800 --> 00:11:36,560
I only did it
because I love you so much.

234
00:11:36,560 --> 00:11:38,040
I lost my head for a moment and then…

235
00:11:38,040 --> 00:11:39,920
I really had no other choice.

236
00:11:41,840 --> 00:11:43,040
I can still have another baby.

237
00:11:43,040 --> 00:11:44,440
This one is gone.

238
00:11:44,440 --> 00:11:46,080
But I can still have another child.

239
00:11:48,320 --> 00:11:49,960
Yao. Dad's here.

240
00:11:51,080 --> 00:11:51,960
Dad.

241
00:11:51,960 --> 00:11:52,640
Yao.

242
00:11:54,520 --> 00:11:55,640
What are you all doing?

243
00:11:55,640 --> 00:11:58,560
[Fang Tao, Fang Yao's Father]
Song Pa, I've been with the group

244
00:11:58,560 --> 00:11:59,840
for more than twenty years.

245
00:11:59,840 --> 00:12:02,640
Always working hard
by your side until now.

246
00:12:03,000 --> 00:12:04,480
Even if I've no merit,
I've put in the effort.

247
00:12:05,680 --> 00:12:06,680
Have you forgotten this?

248
00:12:07,240 --> 00:12:08,280
That year when it was raining,

249
00:12:08,280 --> 00:12:09,200
there was a car crash,

250
00:12:09,720 --> 00:12:11,160
and I was the one who shielded you.

251
00:12:11,560 --> 00:12:12,800
I carried you on my back alone

252
00:12:12,800 --> 00:12:15,080
and walked over ten kilometers
to get you to the hospital.

253
00:12:16,280 --> 00:12:18,120
Now my daughter's been through
all this pain.

254
00:12:18,120 --> 00:12:19,760
Not only do you not compensate her,

255
00:12:20,040 --> 00:12:21,320
but you blame her.

256
00:12:21,720 --> 00:12:22,840
How can you do this to me?

257
00:12:25,240 --> 00:12:27,080
So you're using your daughter

258
00:12:27,080 --> 00:12:28,920
as a bargaining chip for compensation?

259
00:12:28,920 --> 00:12:30,640
Even if my daughter made mistakes,

260
00:12:30,640 --> 00:12:32,400
she's still carrying Ti Cha's child.

261
00:12:33,000 --> 00:12:34,520
Doesn't Ti Cha have any responsibility?

262
00:12:34,520 --> 00:12:35,480
I... I...

263
00:12:35,480 --> 00:12:36,320
Besides,

264
00:12:36,320 --> 00:12:37,840
this is between me and the Song family.

265
00:12:38,200 --> 00:12:39,440
What does it have to do with you?

266
00:12:40,000 --> 00:12:41,360
If you keep stirring things up,

267
00:12:41,520 --> 00:12:42,720
I'll shut you up myself!

268
00:12:42,720 --> 00:12:44,160
Even if you want compensation,

269
00:12:44,480 --> 00:12:46,280
you shouldn't ask Ti Cha for it.

270
00:12:47,240 --> 00:12:48,120
Because,

271
00:12:48,840 --> 00:12:50,640
this child isn't his at all.

